      • pearsonSkewCoef

        public final double pearsonSkewCoef
        A value in range [-1,1] to estimate the skewness of this data set.
        skewness > 0 means it's skewed to right.
        skewness = 0 means it's symmetrical.
        skewness < 0 means it's skewed to left.
